&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Attackers may corrupt metadata of new memory allocated at the address
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May also result in the same effect as some heap overflow vulnerabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
